## Original Work

The original Dutch text *Antirevolutionaire Staatkunde* (1916–1917) by Abraham Kuyper is in the public domain. Kuyper died in 1920, placing the original work beyond copyright in most jurisdictions.

## Translation

This English translation and all scholarly apparatus (indices, companion volumes, annotations, editorial materials) are copyright 2026 by Daniel Metcalf.

